{
  "session_header": "[SESSION_HEADER]\nTimestamp: 1492 DR, Alt 12, 12:00:00\nLocation: The Athenaeum of Lost Voices\nStatus: Lvl 1 Fighter | HP: 12/12 | XP: 0/300 | Gold: 10gp",
  "resources": "HD: 1/1, Potions: 0, Exhaustion: 0",
  "narrative": "Noon (12:00:00) in the Athenaeum of Lost Voices—you take the singed parchment from Brennan's trembling fingers. The parchment is warm to the touch, still carrying the acrid scent of flame. The ink is faded but legible: a hand-drawn map, incomplete, showing the eastern wing of the library with a circle marked in black ink around a section labeled \"Section 7: Restricted.\"\n\n\"Who left this?\" you ask, looking up from the parchment. \"And how did they know which section I was researching?\"\n\nBrennan adjusts his spectacles, his weathered face drawn tight with concern. \"That's what troubles me, lad.\" He lowers his voice, glancing toward the mezzanine. \"Only two others know of your discovery—myself, and Senior Archivist Vaelen. But Vaelen departed for the capital three days past on official business.\"\n\nHe pauses, ears straining toward the shadows between the bookshelves. \"There are... whispers. The Umbral Court has taken an interest in the Seal before. If they've learned of your findings...\"\n\nBrennan doesn't finish. He doesn't need to. The glint of steel catches your eye—in the shadowed alcove near the restricted section entrance, a dagger has been driven into the wooden beam, a folded note pinned beneath it.\n\n[SOCIAL SKILL CHALLENGE: Old Brennan]\nObjective: Learn more about the threat\nNPC Social HP: 5/5 | Status: COOPERATIVE",
  "planning_block": {
    "thinking": "The situation has escalated quickly. Someone knows about my discovery and has left both a warning and an invitation—or a challenge. I need to decide how to proceed with this investigation.",
    "context": "Investigation scene at the Athenaeum",
    "choices": {
      "examine_dagger": {
        "text": "Examine the Dagger",
        "description": "Carefully remove the dagger and read the note without disturbing any fingerprints or evidence",
        "risk_level": "low"
      },
      "interrogate_brennan": {
        "text": "Press Brennan Further",
        "description": "Ask about the Umbral Court and whether there are other suspects in the library",
        "risk_level": "medium"
      },
      "search_vaelen_office": {
        "text": "Search Vaelen's Office",
        "description": "Investigate the missing senior archivist's workspace while Brennan is distracted",
        "risk_level": "high"
      },
      "secure_documents": {
        "text": "Secure Your Research",
        "description": "Return to your workstation and gather all notes about the Seal before they fall into the wrong hands",
        "risk_level": "medium"
      }
    }
  },
  "action_resolution": {
    "player_input": "Investigate the Threat - Examine the singed parchment and question Brennan about who else knows of the Seal",
    "interpreted_as": "investigation_with_social_interaction",
